{
  "info": {
    "name": "FileVault API Collection",
    "description": "Complete API collection for FileVault - Secure Cloud File Storage API\n\n## About FileVault\nFileVault is an enterprise-grade secure file storage solution with:\n- üîí JWT-based authentication with email verification\n- üìÅ Secure file upload/download with AWS S3\n- üõ°Ô∏è Rate limiting and security middleware\n- üìä Comprehensive logging and monitoring\n- üîó Shareable links with expiration controls\n\n## How to Use\n1. **Sign up** for a new account\n2. **Verify email** using the verification token\n3. **Login** to get your JWT token\n4. **Set the token** in the Authorization tab or use {{auth_token}} variable\n5. **Upload files** and manage your storage\n\n## Environment Variables\nSet these variables in Postman:\n- `base_url`: http://localhost:3000\n- `auth_token`: Your JWT token (set automatically after login)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "12345678"
  },
